[package]
name = "joey-mckenzie-tech"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
license = "MIT"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = false

[workspace]
members = [".", "samples/rust/*"]

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.71"
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
hyper = "0.14"
serde_derive = "1"
thiserror = "1"
tracing = "0.1"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.6"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.2.5"
features = ["env"]

[dependencies.config]
version = "0.13"
features = ["toml"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["serde_derive"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.6"
features = ["runtime-tokio-rustls", "postgres", "migrate", "offline", "macros"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.4"
features = ["limit", "timeout", "cors"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.17"
features = ["env-filter"]
